-- EU Close to Approving News Corp.'s BSkyB Takeover, Telegraph Reports
-- B y   R a c h e l   G r a h a m
-- 2010-12-19T11:05:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-19/eu-close-to-approving-news-corp-s-bskyb-deal-telegraph-says.html
The European Commission is close to
approving  News Corp. ’s takeover of  British Sky Broadcasting
Group Plc , the  Sunday Telegraph  reported.  The commission didn’t find any competition problems for the
7.8 billion pound ($12 billion) bid, the report said, citing
unidentified sources familiar with the deal. A final decision
hasn’t yet been made, according to the report.  To contact the reporter on this story:
